HEADWORD: Cuspidor
<hw>Cus"pi*dor</hw> <pr>(-d?r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pg.
<ets>cuspideria</ets>, fr. <ets>cuspir</ets> to spit.]</ety> <def>Any
